<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16000044-rebel-spring"><img alt="Rebel Spring (Falling Kingdoms, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1379031383l/16000044._SX98_.jpg" />
